{
  "texts": [
    "Time series ML analysis is used for forecasting in many different industries.",
    "ML-driven data series analysis can help predict the following: Demand and sales.",
    "ML can help analyze historical data to predict customer demand or sales.",
    "In some cases, there may be a scarcity of historical time series data, making it challenging for ML models to learn meaningful patterns.",
    "In certain cases, time series data may lack clear patterns or trends, making it difficult for ML algorithms to identify meaningful relationships and make accurate predictions."
  ]
}